latestPosts.caption:
In every lifetime, in every universe, l’d choose you as my sister-again and again. You’re the softest part of my heart, the loudest beat in my soul. Har dukh tera khud pe le loon, har khushi tere naam kar doon. You taught me what it means to love without limits, and because of you, I know I can. I’ll stand like a shield between you and every storm. Tu meri jaan hai-my forever, my always.
Happy birthday to my 🌍 @ananyaonlyy

I could write a long caption, but all I want to say is: I love you ❤️🧿
till death do us apart sissy @ananyaonlyy
